        <para> It indicates the type of the input/output data. It support all the integer datatype, number must be between 3 and 8.</para>
        <para> Propriétés : Type 'vec' de taille 1. </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <emphasis role="bold">Number of bits to shift left (use negatif number to shift right)</emphasis>
        </para>
        <para> It indicates the number of bits the input signal is shifted. A positif value indicates a shift left, negatif values indicates shift right.</para>
        <para> Propriétés : Type 'vec' de taille 1. </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <emphasis role="bold">Shifttype(0=Arithmetic 1=Circular)</emphasis>
        </para>
        <para> It indicate the rule used to shift the bits. It can be arithmetic or circular. When the Shifttype is normal, an arithmetic shift is applied to the input signal. In this case, the bits that are shifted.</para>
        <para> Propriétés : Type 'vec' de taille 1.</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
